<h3 id="手动挂载">手动挂载</h3>
<p>将准备好的目录挂在到 merged:</p>





<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl">mount overlay -t overlay -o <span class="nv">lowerdir</span><span class="o">=</span>/root/rootfs-init:/root/rootfs,upperdir<span class="o">=</span>/root/diff,workdir<span class="o">=</span>/root/work /root/merged</span></span></code></pre></div>
<h3 id="使用容器">使用容器</h3>
<p>利用 chroot 改变根文件系统</p>





<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nb">cd</span> merged
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">chroot <span class="nv">$PWD</span> apk update
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">chroot <span class="nv">$PWD</span> apk upgrade
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">chroot <span class="nv">$PWD</span> apk add gcc
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">chroot <span class="nv">$PWD</span> gcc -v
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">chroot <span class="nv">$PWD</span> apk add neofetch
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">chroot <span class="nv">$PWD</span> neofetch</span></span></code></pre></div>
